  "stem": "<figure class=\"table\"><table border=\"1\"><thead><tr><th>x</th><th>y</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>-4</td><td>40</td></tr><tr><td>-2</td><td>32</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td>16</td></tr><tr><td>4</td><td>8</td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>The table shows four values of x and their corresponding values of y. There is a linear relationship between x and y. Which of the following equations represents this relationship?</p>",
