  "rationale": "<p>Slope = (8 - 40)/(4 - (-4)) = -32/8 = -4. Using point (4, 8): 8 = -4(4) + b, so b = 24. The line is y = -4x + 24, or 4x + y = 24. Multiplying by 5 gives 20x + 5y = 120. Choice C is correct.</p>",
